291
00:13:20,150 --> 00:13:20,960
Then,

292
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:23,910
who were they?

293
00:13:25,520 --> 00:13:27,000
Your father, Zhao Li,

294
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,200
was a playboy.

295
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:30,440
He often went to the brothels.

296
00:13:30,910 --> 00:13:32,280
He probably met your mothers there.

297
00:13:41,890 --> 00:13:43,150
Let me explain it in a simple way.

298
00:13:43,150 --> 00:13:44,520
Our mother

299
00:13:44,520 --> 00:13:46,030
is not the same person,

300
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:50,150
but we have the same father.

301
00:13:51,350 --> 00:13:52,640
So, we are a family.

302
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:53,350
Yeah.

303
00:13:53,350 --> 00:13:54,550
A family.

304
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,840
Didn't we agree to tell them the truth?

305
00:14:12,520 --> 00:14:13,760
I would have wanted to.

306
00:14:18,710 --> 00:14:19,790
But when I thought

307
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:22,960
about the connection between Dong Qian and Zou Mian,

308
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:25,960
as well as the case at Fan Tower,

309
00:14:26,110 --> 00:14:27,280
I was afraid that they would keep

310
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:29,280
investigating once they knew the truth.

311
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,520
It'd be dangerous.

312
00:14:34,230 --> 00:14:35,790
How long do you plan to hide it from them?

313
00:14:37,150 --> 00:14:38,320
Play it by ear.

314
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:40,080
Maybe after everything is settled.

315
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:42,280
Dear,

316
00:14:42,350 --> 00:14:43,440
it's pretty late now.

317
00:14:43,520 --> 00:14:45,110
Don't go back to the umbrella shop tonight.

318
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:48,080
I think the orderer will show up again.

319
00:14:54,620 --> 00:14:56,180
[The crimes of Dong Qian are fully recorded here.]

320
00:15:31,350 --> 00:15:32,200
Don't you feel cold?

321
00:15:53,820 --> 00:15:54,960
Is something troubling you?

322
00:16:05,810 --> 00:16:07,960
Do you believe

323
00:16:08,350 --> 00:16:09,470
what they said?

324
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,000
I have no idea.

325
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:18,880
Mo,

326
00:16:20,590 --> 00:16:21,880
should we stop now?

327
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:27,350
I'm also curious about my identity.

328
00:16:29,590 --> 00:16:31,960
When I helped Su to look for her mother,

329
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,380
I also wondered

330
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:37,580
what kind of a woman my mother was.

331
00:16:40,110 --> 00:16:42,280
But I'm also afraid to know the truth.

332
00:16:43,110 --> 00:16:44,550
I wonder if I'd be even sadder

333
00:16:45,790 --> 00:16:47,640
than when I was called a child

334
00:16:47,640 --> 00:16:48,670
without a mother.

335
00:16:51,280 --> 00:16:52,910
I'm not as brave as you are.

336
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:58,470
I'm happy with the life we have now.

337
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:02,550
Since we are living together,

338
00:17:04,110 --> 00:17:05,190
I'm satisfied enough.

339
00:17:07,770 --> 00:17:09,590
Buyou is such an honest man.

340
00:17:11,590 --> 00:17:13,520
Don't torture him anymore, okay?

341
00:17:14,350 --> 00:17:15,280
I feel sorry for him.

342
00:17:18,190 --> 00:17:19,800
If I encounter something,

343
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:21,590
I'll always investigate it

344
00:17:21,590 --> 00:17:22,460
thoroughly.

345
00:17:23,430 --> 00:17:25,230
I always thought I was right.

346
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:28,710
But when I saw Buyou

347
00:17:28,710 --> 00:17:29,590
in an awkward position,

348
00:17:31,590 --> 00:17:32,520
I hesitated.

349
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:35,560
I believe that Buyou has his own reason.

350
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:40,190
Let's wait then.

351
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:41,950
Quit investigating.

352
00:17:42,830 --> 00:17:44,000
Anyway,

353
00:17:44,470 --> 00:17:45,640
I can't find

354
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:47,230
the truth on my own.

355
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:50,070
I won't ask him anymore.

356
00:17:50,070 --> 00:17:50,920
Promise me.

357
00:17:51,430 --> 00:17:52,230
I promise.

358
00:17:52,430 --> 00:17:54,280
Finally, you won't be hard on him.

359
00:17:54,560 --> 00:17:56,590
I didn't want to be hard on him.

360
00:17:56,680 --> 00:17:57,880
Then move back.

361
00:17:58,110 --> 00:17:58,860
He'll be happy

362
00:17:58,860 --> 00:18:00,080
to see you move back.

363
00:18:05,800 --> 00:18:06,800
I'll sleep at home tonight.

364
00:18:12,280 --> 00:18:14,040
Although sometimes you are

365
00:18:14,310 --> 00:18:15,520
quite stubborn

366
00:18:15,520 --> 00:18:16,950
and annoying,

367
00:18:17,950 --> 00:18:19,590
you are always my dear brother.

368
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:20,950
Zhao Ban!

369
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:22,710
Fine,

370
00:18:22,710 --> 00:18:23,470
I'm stubborn

371
00:18:23,470 --> 00:18:24,800
while you are not.

372
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:27,560
Fine, after we buy a new house,

373
00:18:27,560 --> 00:18:28,520
I'll live in the southern-facing room.

374
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:29,400
Anyway,

375
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:30,430
