376
00:18:31,710 --> 00:18:32,230
Wait!

377
00:18:32,230 --> 00:18:33,800
Zhao Mo, Wen Yue agreed to let me

378
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:36,110
live in the southern-facing room.

379
00:18:36,110 --> 00:18:37,000
I don't care.

380
00:18:38,560 --> 00:18:39,400
Zhao Mo!

381
00:18:39,760 --> 00:18:41,350
How could you do this?

382
00:18:44,310 --> 00:18:46,000
Bed time.

383
00:18:47,070 --> 00:18:48,110
- Bed time. - Ban.

384
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:50,110
What's this?

385
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,880
This is called trotting horse lamp.

386
00:18:53,310 --> 00:18:54,950
Mo made it for me.

387
00:18:54,950 --> 00:18:56,590
Mo is so clever.

388
00:18:59,590 --> 00:19:00,680
He is

389
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:02,110
sometimes clever

390
00:19:03,070 --> 00:19:04,920
but sometimes stupid.

391
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:08,190
Sometimes he treats me well,

392
00:19:10,190 --> 00:19:11,950
but sometimes he goes against me.

393
00:19:13,950 --> 00:19:14,950
He's pretty complicated.

394
00:19:16,070 --> 00:19:16,880
Ban,

395
00:19:18,950 --> 00:19:21,070
who gave you these then?

396
00:19:22,190 --> 00:19:23,160
This

397
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:25,400
was given by my father.

398
00:19:26,350 --> 00:19:27,520
It's pretty old.

399
00:19:28,470 --> 00:19:30,430
This was given by Buyou.

400
00:19:32,310 --> 00:19:33,280
They always

401
00:19:33,280 --> 00:19:35,310
think I'm a child

402
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,310
who can never be mature.

403
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:38,310
Ban,

404
00:19:38,310 --> 00:19:40,190
are you mature enough now?

405
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:41,950
Not yet.

406
00:19:45,190 --> 00:19:46,110
Ban,

407
00:19:46,920 --> 00:19:48,400
why are there

408
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:50,920
so many herbs in your room?

409
00:19:53,070 --> 00:19:54,520
Because I always

410
00:19:54,520 --> 00:19:56,520
want to be a physician.

411
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,400
Wen Yue supports me.

412
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:00,800
She prepared these for me.

413
00:20:01,760 --> 00:20:03,560
But I failed

414
00:20:03,560 --> 00:20:04,590
to be a physician.

415
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,680
Then I felt

416
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,640
that I could be a coroner.

417
00:20:09,110 --> 00:20:10,350
Wen Yue

418
00:20:10,800 --> 00:20:11,710
still

419
00:20:12,110 --> 00:20:13,590
supports me.

420
00:20:13,590 --> 00:20:15,710
So, I became a coroner.

421
00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:19,120
What do you want to be?

422
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:36,600
Su,

423
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:38,620
don't worry.

424
00:20:39,710 --> 00:20:42,100
I've already found out the "Ci Rou"

425
00:20:42,520 --> 00:20:43,800
your mother embroidered on the handkerchief.

426
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,680
I will go ask about it tomorrow.

427
00:20:56,830 --> 00:20:57,920
Why aren't my name and Ban's name

428
00:20:57,920 --> 00:20:59,310
