435
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:46,520
Run!

436
00:21:50,470 --> 00:21:51,760
Mother!

437
00:22:14,430 --> 00:22:15,110
Ban,

438
00:22:15,110 --> 00:22:16,470
you are leaving so early.

439
00:22:16,560 --> 00:22:17,830
You are early, too.

440
00:22:18,560 --> 00:22:19,350
Ban.

441
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:21,800
Yao He?

442
00:22:23,470 --> 00:22:24,710
Are you

443
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:26,680
going to work or have you just finished it?

444
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:27,590
Just finished my work.

445
00:22:27,590 --> 00:22:28,800
Just finished it?

446
00:22:28,800 --> 00:22:30,070
Why so late?

447
00:22:30,760 --> 00:22:32,160
Did you conduct an autopsy last night?

448
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,110
Why didn't you call me?

449
00:22:33,110 --> 00:22:34,280
No,

450
00:22:34,280 --> 00:22:36,310
how dare I conduct an autopsy alone at night?

451
00:22:38,110 --> 00:22:39,310
So what did you do last night?

452
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:41,280
I went to the court

453
00:22:41,280 --> 00:22:43,430
and copied the autopsy record.

454
00:22:43,880 --> 00:22:45,430
I fell asleep as I was so tired.

455
00:22:45,880 --> 00:22:46,350
You know what?

456
00:22:46,350 --> 00:22:48,040
There were a lot of mosquitoes.

457
00:22:48,230 --> 00:22:49,520
That's why I came back till now.

458
00:22:51,280 --> 00:22:53,430
You may sleep in the autopsy room

459
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:55,000
which has much fewer mosquitoes.

460
00:22:57,280 --> 00:22:59,020
Mosquitoes don't often bite me anyway.

461
00:22:59,230 --> 00:23:00,190
Where are you going?

462
00:23:00,430 --> 00:23:02,560
I will look for clues about Su's mother.

463
00:23:02,560 --> 00:23:03,800
I have to go.

464
00:23:03,800 --> 00:23:04,830
Let me go with you.

465
00:23:04,890 --> 00:23:06,070
No, I'm good.

466
00:23:06,070 --> 00:23:07,190
Just go home and have a rest.

467
00:23:07,190 --> 00:23:08,230
I'm fine. I often

468
00:23:08,230 --> 00:23:09,070
stayed up.

469
00:23:09,430 --> 00:23:11,070
No.

470
00:23:11,070 --> 00:23:12,280
If you die,

471
00:23:12,280 --> 00:23:14,110
who will teach me then?

472
00:23:15,110 --> 00:23:15,830
Are you sure you go alone?

473
00:23:15,830 --> 00:23:17,000
Yes, I'm sure.

474
00:23:17,430 --> 00:23:17,920
Okay,

475
00:23:18,000 --> 00:23:18,920
see you then.

476
00:23:19,660 --> 00:23:20,370
See you.

477
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:24,020
Ban,

478
00:23:28,310 --> 00:23:29,310
I will cook for you.

479
00:23:30,110 --> 00:23:30,920
Okay.

480
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,570
See you.

481
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:41,300
- Your ox is good. - Look.

482
00:23:41,300 --> 00:23:43,210
Yes, I fed them with good grains.

483
00:23:43,520 --> 00:23:44,210
It's surely strong.

484
00:23:44,680 --> 00:23:45,180
Really?

485
00:23:45,180 --> 00:23:46,920
Yeah, it eats good grains.

486
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:48,090
It eats what I eat.

487
00:23:48,090 --> 00:23:49,320
What are you chatting about?

488
00:23:50,460 --> 00:23:51,300
Your ox is good.

489
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:55,350
Little rooster, you are so beautiful.

490
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:56,470
Yeah?

491
00:23:57,350 --> 00:23:58,560
I raised it.

492
00:23:59,280 --> 00:24:00,160
Beautiful.

493
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:01,640
Its feather looks so nice.

494
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:02,520
Yeah.

495
00:24:10,830 --> 00:24:11,680
Morning.

496
00:24:11,680 --> 00:24:12,190
You are up?

497
00:24:13,710 --> 00:24:14,190
Father,

498
00:24:15,190 --> 00:24:17,230
why are Mo and Ban both not at home?

499
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:19,350
I have no idea.

500
00:24:19,640 --> 00:24:20,800
Well,

501
00:24:20,800 --> 00:24:22,920
Mo went to work.

502
00:24:23,560 --> 00:24:26,230
I had a dream about my mother last night

503
00:24:26,680 --> 00:24:27,920
and cried bitterly.

504
00:24:28,110 --> 00:24:29,950
To comfort me,

505
00:24:29,950 --> 00:24:31,710
Ban went to look for my mother.

506
00:24:35,710 --> 00:24:37,920
Little rooster, come out.

507
00:24:37,920 --> 00:24:39,040
Come out.

508
00:24:48,700 --> 00:24:55,540
[Ci Rou Women's Mutual Aid Society]

509
00:25:01,070 --> 00:25:02,400
Hello! Anyone here?

510
00:25:18,070 --> 00:25:19,040
Lady.

511
00:25:23,280 --> 00:25:24,920
May I help you?

512
00:25:27,190 --> 00:25:28,350
I wonder if this handkerchief

513
00:25:28,350 --> 00:25:29,800
