516
00:25:37,590 --> 00:25:39,310
How did you get it?

517
00:25:40,520 --> 00:25:42,230
It was left by Ci

518
00:25:42,230 --> 00:25:44,400
and Song Yingying.

519
00:25:44,830 --> 00:25:46,590
I'd like to know about them.

520
00:25:46,710 --> 00:25:47,920
That's why I came here.

521
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:51,470
So, you were introduced by Ci and Yingying.

522
00:25:52,230 --> 00:25:54,070
Let's go to the rear hall then.

523
00:25:54,230 --> 00:25:56,560
Let's have some tea and talk about the details.

524
00:25:57,310 --> 00:25:59,110
Have they come here recently?

525
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:00,190
I was just asking.

526
00:26:00,190 --> 00:26:02,160
All of our members are close.

527
00:26:02,160 --> 00:26:04,400
How can I just let you stand here to talk?

528
00:26:04,830 --> 00:26:05,710
Lady,

529
00:26:05,710 --> 00:26:06,350
please.

530
00:26:20,800 --> 00:26:21,880
Gu,

531
00:26:22,230 --> 00:26:23,760
any news about those two people?

532
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:25,950
Ban went to look for Ci again.

533
00:26:26,190 --> 00:26:27,430
After all, Ci's a suspect,

534
00:26:27,880 --> 00:26:28,920
and I feel a bit worried.

535
00:26:29,160 --> 00:26:30,280
Have you posted their

536
00:26:30,280 --> 00:26:31,070
wanted notice?

537
00:26:31,310 --> 00:26:32,070
Yes.

538
00:26:37,280 --> 00:26:37,920
Boss.

539
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:38,350
We went

540
00:26:38,350 --> 00:26:40,190
to the homes of the missing girls

541
00:26:40,470 --> 00:26:41,680
and found this

542
00:26:42,710 --> 00:26:43,950
in many of their homes.

543
00:26:44,780 --> 00:26:46,640
[Ci Rou]

544
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:47,520
Go away.

545
00:26:56,190 --> 00:26:57,760
What does Ci Rou mean?

546
00:26:57,760 --> 00:26:58,470
It seems

547
00:26:58,470 --> 00:27:00,830
to be a place where women are taught needlework,

548
00:27:00,950 --> 00:27:01,830
located in Wuxue Alley.

549
00:27:04,920 --> 00:27:06,280
I saw this once

550
00:27:06,760 --> 00:27:07,640
in the embroidery workshop.

551
00:27:08,070 --> 00:27:10,230
Ban also saw one in Song Yingying's room.

552
00:27:11,470 --> 00:27:12,640
She said Ci also has one.

553
00:27:14,040 --> 00:27:14,830
Crap,

554
00:27:16,350 --> 00:27:17,430
go to Wuxue Alley.

555
00:27:17,430 --> 00:27:18,000
Yes.

556
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:22,470
Ci Rou Women's Mutual Aid Society

557
00:27:22,470 --> 00:27:25,000
is specifically dedicated to helping orphaned girls, homeless women,

558
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:26,040
and those from poor families,

559
00:27:26,040 --> 00:27:28,040
providing them with skills training.

560
00:27:28,400 --> 00:27:29,190
If one can do it well,

561
00:27:29,190 --> 00:27:31,190
she can run a business

562
00:27:31,190 --> 00:27:32,640
just like Yingying and Ci.

563
00:27:33,110 --> 00:27:33,730
At least,

564
00:27:34,310 --> 00:27:35,820
she can make a living with these skills.

565
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:40,160
You look beautiful.

566
00:27:40,310 --> 00:27:42,110
That's your born strength.

567
00:27:42,520 --> 00:27:43,920
Thank you.

568
00:27:45,280 --> 00:27:46,560
I'd like to ask you

569
00:27:46,560 --> 00:27:49,280
when you saw Ci last time.

570
00:27:49,710 --> 00:27:50,710
Three days ago.

571
00:27:52,230 --> 00:27:53,640
Three days ago...

572
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:55,230
When she came here...

573
00:27:55,280 --> 00:27:56,950
Today's tea is so good.

574
00:27:57,040 --> 00:27:58,430
Why don't you have some?

575
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:19,040
When she came here three days ago,

576
00:28:19,040 --> 00:28:20,640
what did she do?

577
00:28:21,040 --> 00:28:22,590
As you did,

578
00:28:23,590 --> 00:28:24,830
she came to ask about Yingying.

579
00:28:25,190 --> 00:28:26,350
Ask about Yingying?

580
00:28:31,190 --> 00:28:32,070
No way.

581
00:28:33,280 --> 00:28:34,280
Yingying had already...

582
00:28:34,280 --> 00:28:36,400
Yingying had already died by that time.

583
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:37,310
Right?

584
00:28:40,310 --> 00:28:42,190
